Require agentgrep

Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui.gif
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui.mp4
Output docs/_static/demos/vhs/agentgrep-ui.webm

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1900
Set Height 700
Source docs/_static/demos/vhs/_preamble.tape

Sleep 1s
Type "agentgrep ui"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "retry"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s
Down
Sleep 300ms
Down
Sleep 300ms
Type "j"
Sleep 1500ms
Type "j"
Sleep 1500ms
Type "j"
Sleep 1500ms
Ctrl+L
Sleep 1800ms
Ctrl+H
Sleep 1200ms
Ctrl+C
Sleep 350ms
Ctrl+C
Wait
Sleep 1500ms
